               <item n="project_comment_old">&lt;p&gt;[[Broomhead I]]: 121 has notes and translates: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;a1 [The] immeasurable vedanā, also [is] there exactly the same &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;a2 There also in just this way [is] the correct ... &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;a3 In just this way the correct 'exertions' are to be performed. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;a4 The smṛtyupasthānas are to be perfomed [and] by every single on ethis very ... &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;b1 There is also in just this way correct 'releases' to be done. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;b2 The smṛtyupasthānas are to be performed [and] by every single one [this very] ... &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;b3 ... are to be trusted exactly as with the four smṛtyupasthānas. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;b4 ... is burning with passion [and] with hatred [also] it is burning. &lt;/p&gt;</item>
